# FSERP VPS deploy

When the user asks how to deploy, update, or restart on the VPS, give **only** these commands (no alternatives unless they explicitly ask):

```bash
cd ~/fserp/fserp
git pull
bash scripts/deploy-vps.sh
```

Do not list manual migrate/build/PM2 steps, quick-restart variants, or frontend-only/backend-only paths unless the user explicitly requests a different workflow.
